(At the time of capture, metrics for `node2`, `node3`, and some worker-hosted pods were still incomplete even though the pods) Tj
T*
(themselves were healthy and the services were reachable. The right-sizing decision therefore combines:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. live measurements that were available) Tj
T*
(2. confirmed healthy pod placement across the cluster) Tj
T*
(3. PVC-backed storage status) Tj
T*
(4. known node capacity from the lease-backed `m1.large` deployment) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(That is sufficient to justify the selected requests and limits for the milestone-scale Q2 workload.) Tj
ET
